ul.li: AWS Lambda@Edge inspects every incoming request to CloudFront and ensures the request has a valid JWT in the cookies.
Only requests with a valid JWT will be forwarded to Amazon S3 (or whatever origin you run behind CloudFront)
Requests without a valid JWT will be redirected to the Cognito Hosted UI where the user must first sign-in
After sign-in, the JWTs will be set in cookies, and sent by the user agent automatically with subsequent requests
